        • Once Daily Probiotics for Women: Our probiotic is designed specifically for feminine health & overall digestive health. 6 diverse strains (50B CFU), D-Mannose, Pro-Cran, & organic prebiotics provide you with the feminine support you deserve.

        Product Description

        Once Daily Prebiotic/Probiotic Blend for Women

        With 50 billion CFUs of probiotics, prebiotics, and powerful ingredients including cranberry extract and D-mannose, Physician’s Choice Women’s Probiotic provides an optimally balanced, all-in-one formula in a delayed-release capsule to support digestive, immune, and urinary system health*.

        Technology for an Impenetrable Barrier Against Moisture, Oxygen, and Light.

        • Desiccant surrounds the product and absorbs any moisture
        • Enteric coated capsules ensure live culture potency

        Proanthocyanadins from cranberry are well-studied for supporting a healthy urinary system⁴*

        A concentrated dose of D-Mannose offers potent benefits to maintain urinary tract health⁵*

        Our Prebiotic Blend supplies organic soluble fiber from Acacia Senegal and Jerusalem Artichoke to enhance the viability and function of probiotic organisms⁶*

            Important information

            Safety Information

            Keep out of reach of children. Do not use if safety seal is damaged or missing. Store in a cool, dry place. Pregnant women, lactating women, and anyone taking medications, should consult a health care professional before using any nutritional product. If any adverse reactions occur, discontinue use and consult a health care professional.

            Ingredients

            Probiotic Women's Blend 50 Billion CFU: Lactobacillus plantarum, Lactobacillus paracasei, Lactobacillus casei, Lactobacillus gasseri, Lactobacillus acidophilus, Bifidobacterium lactis, Prebiotic Blend: Organic Jerusalem Artichoke Root, Organic Gum Arabic (Fibergum), D-Mannose, Cranberry Extract (Pro Cran d'Or), Rice Flour, Vegetable Capsule (Hypromellose, Gellum Gum), Rice Hulls Extract, Gum Arabic, and Sunflower Oil.

            Directions

            As a dietary supplement, take one (1) veggie capsule once a day.
